name: Moostache Support
body:
# Moostache

The most fun mustache sticker pack in the app store. Lighten up your conversations with 48 different mustache stickers. 

# Stickers

Stickers are completely static and do not collect any personal data from your phone.

# Moostache App Support

If you would like to get support for Moostache or have any questions/comments please email support@burag.com with a subject line: Moostache App Support
